com.energyxxer.commodore.types

Class TypeAssert

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.energyxxer.commodore.types.TypeAssert

  • public class TypeAssert
extends java.lang.Object
    Utility class whose purpose is to aid commands to validate types passed as parameters.
    As the standard is to never use Type subclasses to narrow down possible types, and instead compare types via their Type.category value, this class' methods do just that, throwing an exception if a type is not of a desired type.
